","msg":"一人一Post狂洗連登 [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\nTG群組，不停轉發出去，勢要討回雙眼，嬲到火屎呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群好多人入緊：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpnwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=31d3fc5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n睇消息去實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpnwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=eae81113\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"15c2da72024046ae595ab37ad18f489e23997bee","tid":1449581,"uid":279111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:13:31.000Z","msg":"屌推唔起"},{"pid":"aa425afe9e93597d3621ba2cb22c6107c1f61c07","tid":1449581,"uid":279111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:13:42.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"20a95a6d35474d69c09494c863b70af7387e201a","tid":1449581,"uid":279111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:13:53.000Z","msg":"811"},{"pid":"fcdb6a12e4967ae77ce5cdb34fddc6b677db3559","tid":1449581,"uid":279111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:14:05.000Z","msg":"811 恐襲"},{"pid":"6b94dbca05f0f62e1415b9fd19a1c883f0f0ec1e","tid":1449581,"uid":44312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:14:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;